                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@foreveronefashion?_r=1&_t=ZS-94bnu6iArP3" class="w-10 h-10 border border-gold/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-gold hover:bg-gold hover:text-black transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg shadow-gold/5">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12.525.02c1.31-.02 2.61-.01 3.91-.02.08 1.53.63 3.09 1.75 4.17 1.12 1.11 2.7 1.62 4.24 1.79v4.03c-1.44-.17-2.86-.6-4.12-1.31a6.417 6.417 0 01-1.87-1.54v8.13c.01 2.15-.45 4.33-1.74 6.02-1.31 1.73-3.43 2.78-5.57 2.69-2.23-.05-4.43-1.12-5.74-2.93-1.31-1.81-1.58-4.22-.73-6.28.84-2.03 2.87-3.53 5.06-3.72v4.05c-1.28.11-2.52.84-3.13 1.96-.61 1.12-.5 2.54.29 3.5.79.97 2.11 1.35 3.3.97 1.19-.38 2.02-1.53 2.02-2.78V.02z"/></svg>
                    </a>
